  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "太史公讀秦記，至犬戎敗幽王，周東徙洛邑，秦襄公始封為諸侯，作西畤用事上帝，僭端見矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "《禮》曰：「天子祭天地，諸侯祭其域內名山大川。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "」今秦雜戎翟之俗，先暴戾，後仁義，位在藩臣而臚於郊祀，君子懼焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "及文公踰隴，攘夷狄，尊陳寶，營岐雍之閒，而穆公修政，東竟至河，則與齊桓、晉文中國侯伯侔矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "是後陪臣執政，大夫世祿，六卿擅晉權，征伐會盟，威重於諸侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "及田常殺簡公而相齊國，諸侯晏然弗討，海內爭於戰功矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "三國終之卒分晉，田和亦滅齊而有之，六國之盛自此始。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "務在彊兵并敵，謀詐用而從衡短長之說起。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "矯稱蜂出，誓盟不信，雖置質剖符猶不能約束也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "秦始小國僻遠，諸夏賓之，比於戎翟，至獻公之後常雄諸侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "論秦之德義不如魯衛之暴戾者，量秦之兵不如三晉之彊也，然卒并天下，非必險固便形勢利也，蓋若天所助焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "或曰「東方物所始生，西方物之成孰」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "夫作事者必於東南，收功實者常於西北。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "故禹興於西羌，湯起於亳，周之王也以豐鎬伐殷，秦之帝用雍州興，漢之興自蜀漢。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "秦既得意，燒天下詩書，諸侯史記尤甚，為其有所刺譏也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "詩書所以復見者，多藏人家，而史記獨藏周室，以故滅。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "惜哉，惜哉！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "獨有秦記，又不載日月，其文略不具。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "然戰國之權變亦有可頗采者，何必上古。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "秦取天下多暴，然世異變，成功大。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "傳曰「法後王」，何也？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "以其近己而俗變相類，議卑而易行也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "學者牽於所聞，見秦在帝位日淺，不察其終始，因舉而笑之，不敢道，此與以耳食無異。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "悲夫！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "余於是因秦記，踵春秋之後，起周元王，表六國時事，訖二世，凡二百七十年，著諸所聞興壞之端。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "後有君子，以覽觀焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "公元前476 周元王元年。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "秦厲共公元年。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "魏獻子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "衛出公輒後元年。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "韓宣子 趙簡子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "四十二。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "楚惠王章十三年。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "吳伐我。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "燕獻公十七年。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "齊平公驁五年。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
